WEBVTT

00:03:30.600 --> 00:03:31.800
by terrorists,

00:03:32.760 --> 00:03:33.960
by criminals.

00:03:34.920 --> 00:03:36.960
Weapons can do a lot of harm.

00:03:38.040 --> 00:03:40.280
They are the cause of much distress.

00:03:41.080 --> 00:03:45.120
Why then am I standing before you
with this weapon?

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:50.040
Why did I choose the gun as my instrument?

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.400
Today I want to tell you why.

00:03:54.160 --> 00:03:55.736
Today I want to tell you

00:03:55.760 --> 00:03:58.720
why I chose the gun
to create a better world.

00:03:59.680 --> 00:04:03.840
And I want to tell you
how this gun can help.